title: Dog And Beth On The Hunt S02E07 Rude Awakening WS DSR x264-[NY2]
description:
When Dog and Beth visit Leland on the Big Island, their vacation quickly turns into a hunt. Leland has two tough jumps in the rural wilds of Hilo. There are a lot of places to hide in the backcountry, but you don't want to be caught napping if Dog's in town. Can Dog turn the fugitive's dreams of freedom into a rude awakening?

thanks to capper and poster
